# Artifact Sync (required)

Every non-trivial change MUST update the full sync surface in the **same** change. Incomplete sync = not done.

## Sync matrix

| If you change… | Also update… |
|----------------|--------------|
| Behavior / UX / RPC / RLS | `openspec/specs/` (or active change + archive) |
| Routes, ops, architecture | Matching `docs/**` (spec, ops, playbook, navigation) |
| Feature / bugfix | Tests (`regression_*` for bugs) per `tests-required` |
| Recurring convention | `.cursor/skills/*/SKILL.md` and/or `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` |
| Role scope / escalation | `.cursor/agents/*.md` + root `AGENTS.md` |

## Exempt (document in PR/commit if skipping OpenSpec)

Typos, pure refactors with zero behavior change, dependency bumps only.

## Before finishing

1. Run skill `edunudg-sync-artifacts` checklist
2. Confirm Definition of Done sync section
3. Do **not** leave “docs/tests later” TODOs for sync items
